ogy</a></li><li><a href="https://www.rmit.edu.au/partner/recruit-students-and-graduates" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RMIT University</a></li><li><a href="http://scu.edu.au/students/index.php/92" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Southern Cross University</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><ul><li><a href="http://www.swinburne.edu.au/corporate/careers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Swinburne University of Technology</a></li><li><a href="http://careers.anu.edu.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Australian National University</a></li><li><a href="https://www.auckland.ac.nz/en/for/current-students/career-development-and-employment-services.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Auckland - Waipapa Taumata Rau</a></li><li><a href="http://careers.unimelb.edu.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Melbourne</a></li><li><a href="http://www.newcastle.edu.au/current-students/support/careers-jobs-and-your-future" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Newcastle</a></li><li><a href="http://www.uq.edu.au/uqadvantage/careers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Queensland</a></li><li><a href="http://sydney.edu.au/careers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Sydney</a></li><li><a href="http://sydney.edu.au/business/careers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Sydney Business School</a></li><li><a href="http://www.careers.uwa.edu.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The University of Western Australia</a></li><li><a href="https://studenthub.torrens.edu.au/Hub/careers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Torrens University Australia</a></li><li><a href="http://www.canberra.edu.au/current-students/careers-service" target="_blank" rel="noopener">University of Canberra</a></li><li><a href="https://www.otago.ac.nz/" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">University of Otago</a></li><li><a href="https://www.unisq.edu.au/current-students/support/career-development" target="_blank" rel="noopener">University of Southern Queensland</a></li><li><a href="http://www.uts.edu.au/partners-and-community/working-uts/recruit/services-employers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">University of Technology, Sydney</a></li><li><a href="https://www.uow.edu.au/careers/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">University of Wollongong</a></li><li><a href="http://www.careers.unsw.edu.au/" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UNSW Sydney</a></li><li><a href="https://www.business.unsw.edu.au/students/career-accelerator/internships/connecting-with-our-students" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">UNSW Sydney (AGSM &amp; UNSW Business School)</a><a href="https://www.uow.edu.au/careers/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><br></a><a href="https://www.vu.edu.au/current-students/careers-opportunities/careers-advice" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Victoria University</a></li><li><a href="http://www.westernsydney.edu.au/careers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Western Sydney University</a></li><li><br></li></ul></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><h3>High School Members</h3><p>High schools are also welcomed as members of our community.</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.ravenswood.nsw.edu.au/" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ravenswood School for Girls</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
INSERT INTO pages (slug, title, content, requires_auth, show_in_nav, nav_position, published) VALUES ('events', 'Events', '<div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><h1>Learning, sharing and networking for early careers professionals</h1></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join us</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div><!-- /content zone --><!-- footer zone --><div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Events</p></div></div><div ><div> The AAGE offers fantasic opportunities for learning, sharing and networking around the country each year where members benefit from complimentary or discounted attendance.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>Annual AAGE Conference</p></div></div><div ><div><p>This event brings together early careers practitioners from around Australia, offering professional and personal development.</p></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=conference" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Learn more</a></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div><p>The Big Meet</p></div></div><div ><div><p>The Big Meet careers fairs offer exhibitors the opportunity&nbsp;to effectively connect with potential candidates from all universities at once. Members can access substantial exhibitor discounts.</p></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=the-big-meet" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Roundtables</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Held in Adelaide, Brisbane, Canberra, Melbourne, Perth, Sydney and virtually, our Roundtables are free for members and offer wonderful opportunities for knowledge sharing and peer connection.</p></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=annual-event-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View event calendar</a></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div><p>Industry Videoconferences</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Industry-specific videoconferences enable employer members to connect and share with their peers, regardless of location.</p></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=annual-event-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View event calendar</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Webinars</p></div></div><div ><div><p>AAGE webinars are free for members and offer&nbsp;thought leadership, market intelligence and actionable insights.</p></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=annual-event-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View event calendar</a>&nbsp;</div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div><p>Industry Conferences</p></div></div><div ><div> Annual conferences coordinated by our international counterparts in the global early careers space.</div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=industry-events" target="_blank" rel="noopener">View conferences</a></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
INSERT INTO pages (slug, title, content, requires_auth, show_in_nav, nav_position, published) VALUES ('upcoming-events', 'Upcoming Events', '<div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><h1>Register to attend or exhibit at upcoming AAGE events</h1></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join us</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div><!-- /content zone --><!-- footer zone --><div><div><div><div ><div><p>Upcoming AAGE events</p></div></div><div ><div ><ul><li><span >Australia/Brisbane</span><div><a href="/events.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Brisbane</a></div><div><span client-tz-display client-tz-item="Australia/Brisbane" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)">05 May 2026 12:00 PM</span></div><div><span>Mallesons - Level 33, One Eagle Waterfront Brisbane, 1 Eagle Street, Brisbane</span></div></li><li><span >Australia/Sydney</span><div><a href="/events.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Graduate Managers Forum, Canberra - May 2026</a></div><div><span client-tz-display client-tz-item="Australia/Sydney" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)">07 May 2026 11:00 AM</span></div><div><span>Department of the Treasury - 1 Langton Crescent, Canberra</span></div></li><li><span >Australia/Sydney</span><div><a href="/events.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Canberra</a></div><div><span client-tz-display client-tz-item="Australia/Sydney" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)">07 May 2026 12:00 PM</span></div><div><span>Department of the Treasury - 1 Langton Crescent, Canberra</span></div></li><li><span >Australia/Adelaide</span><div><a href="/events.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Adelaide</a></div><div><span client-tz-display client-tz-item="Australia/Adelaide" client-tz-formatted=" (ACST)">12 May 2026 12:00 PM</span><