6, 11:00 AM 12:00 PM Department of the Treasury - 1 Langton Crescent, Canberra" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Graduate Managers Forum, Canberra - May 2026</a><br />May 07 <a href="/events.html" client-tz-item="Australia/Sydney" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)" title="n[]07 May 2026, 12:00 PM 2:00 PM Department of the Treasury - 1 Langton Crescent, Canberra" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Canberra</a><br />May 12 <a href="/events.html" client-tz-item="Australia/Adelaide" client-tz-formatted=" (ACST)" title="n[]12 May 2026, 12:00 PM 2:00 PM CPA Australia - Level 10, 420 King William Street, Adelaide" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Adelaide</a><br />May 13 <a href="/events.html" client-tz-item="Australia/Perth" client-tz-formatted=" (AWST)" title="n[]13 May 2026, 12:00 PM 2:00 PM Office of Digital Government - Dumas House, 2 Havelock Street, West Perth" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Perth</a><br />May 19 <a href="/events.html" client-tz-item="Australia/Sydney" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)" title="n[]19 May 2026, 12:00 PM 2:30 PM Chartered Accountants Australia and New Zealand - Ground Floor, 600 Bourke Street, Melbourne" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Melbourne</a><br />May 20 <a href="/events.html" client-tz-item="Australia/Sydney" client-tz-formatted=" (AEST)" title="n[]20 May 2026, 12:00 PM 2:30 PM Sofitel Sydney Wentworth - Level 4, Adelaide Room, 61-101 Phillip Street, Sydney (entrance via Phillip Street or Bligh Street)" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2026 AAGE Guest Presentation and Member Discussion - Sydney</a></td><td><a href="/page.html?slug=annual-event-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">June</a></td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td><a href="/page.html?slug=annual-event-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener">July</a></td><td><a href="/page.html?slug=an