>FINALISTS: </strong>Fusion Graduate Consultancy and GradConnection</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Careers Service<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by employers participating in the 2014 AGRIAs voting process)</p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Curtin University of Technology</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>University of Adelaide, University of Queensland and University of Wollongong</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Contribution to the Graduate Recruitment and Development Industry<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by employers participating in the 2014 AGRIAs voting process)</p><p><strong></strong></p><strong>JOINT WINNERS: </strong>David Cvetkovski - Fusion Graduate Consultancy and Mike Casey - GradConnection<p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Graduate Development Program<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by graduates participating in the 2014 AAGE Graduate Survey))</p><p><strong></strong></p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>ExxonMobil</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>SA Power Networks and SA Water Corporation</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Most Popular Exhibitor at the AAGE Conference<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2014 AAGE Conference Delegates)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong><span>Revelian</span></p><p><strong>FINALISTS:&nbsp;</strong><span>Grad App, GradConnection</span></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/agrias3-373px-e57698cc-efb29902.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/agrias1-373px-d997ae39-0580842c.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></d