rket <br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as voted by our judging panel)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Queensland Rail</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>L''Oreal Australia, PricewaterhouseCoopers</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Graduate Development Program <br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as voted by our judging panel)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>BHP Billiton</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>Department of Finance and Deregulation, Pitcher Partners</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Careers Service for Employers<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2011 AAGE Employer Survey responses)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Monash University</p><p><strong>FINALISTS:</strong> Curtin University of Technology, The University of Queensland, The University of Sydney, Faculty of Economics &amp; Business, University of New South Wales, University of Technology, Sydney</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Supplier to the Graduate Recruitment Industry</p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2011 AAGE Employer Survey responses)</p><p><strong>WINNER:</strong> Unimail</p><p><strong>FINALIST:</strong> GradConnection</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div> Award for Best Contribution to the Graduate Recruitment Industry</div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2011 AAGE Employer Survey responses)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Ben Reeves, Australian Association of Graduate Employers</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>Andrea Culligan, Unimail, David Cvetkovski, Fusion Graduate Management Solutions, Kate Fizzell, Unimail</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Graduate Recruiter of the Year<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2011 AAGE Candidate Survey responses)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Hayley Warne, GE Capital Finance Australasia</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>Elise Ianno, Deloitte, Elissa Hadgkiss, Department of Finance and Deregulation, Samantha Walton, Deloitte</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Aspirational Employer of the Year<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2011 AAGE Candidate Survey responses)</p><p><strong>WINNER:</strong> Google</p><p><strong>FINALISTS:</strong> Australian Taxation Office, Deloitte, KPMG, Macquarie Group</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>Award for Best Exhibitor<br></p></div></div><div ><div><p>(as determined by 2010 AAGE Conference delegate votes)</p><p><strong>WINNER: </strong>Unimail</p><p><strong>FINALISTS: </strong>GradConnection, Onetest</p><p><strong></strong></p></div></div><div ><div><p>AAGE Hall of Fame Award<br></p></div></div><div ><div><strong>RECIPIENT:</strong> Naomi McQuaid, AGRF<p><strong></strong></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/agrias3-373px-e57698cc-efb29902.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/agrias1-373px-d997ae39-0580842c.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div><div ><div></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div ><div><p><br></p></div></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
INSERT INTO pages (slug, title, content, requires_auth, show_in_nav, nav_position, published) VALUES ('amberjackglobal', 'Amberjack Global', '<div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><h1>Helping shape the future of early careers through industry partnerships</h1></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join us</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div><!-- /content zone --><!-- footer zone --><div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Industry Partner Profile</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Amberjack Global</p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>Amberjack Global (formally Fusion Graduate Consultancy) is a trusted leader in Early Careers, with over 25 years of experience and a long-standing team of experts dedicated to shaping the future of early talent. We combine deep industry insight with innovative technology to deliver tailored solutions that help organisations attract, assess, select, and develop talent.</p><p>Since joining the Amberjack Global Group in 2023, our APAC capability has been significantly strengthened - expanding access to global insights, advanced technologies, and specialist expertise. This integration enables us to offer the best of both worlds: world-class innovation paired with a strong local understanding of early talent across Australia and New Zealand.</p><p>Our award-winning approach is built on our unique Potential Framework, ensuring fairness, consistency, and predictive validity across every stage of the hiring process. From targeted attraction campaigns to adaptive assessments and customised development programs, we support organisations at any point in the talent journey.</p><p>Amberjack supports clients end-to-end or at any specific point of challenge, acting as a seamless extension of your HR team. With full visibility and control, we help drive long-term performance while empowering individuals to build meaningful and successful careers.</p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/1-0-amberjack-4e74d910-73bf2dff.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div ><div><p>Contact details</p></div></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="mailto:info@weareamberjack.com.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Email</a>&nbsp;<br></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="https://weareamberjack.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Website</a>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/showcase/amberjack-global-apac/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="tel:+61411115134" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tel:&nbsp;0411 115 134</a></p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
INSERT INTO pages (slug, title, content, requires_auth, show_in_nav, nav_position, published) VALUES ('bechallenged', 'Be Challenged', '<div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><h1>Helping shape the future of early careers through industry partnerships</h1></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join us</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div><!-- /content zone --><!-- footer zone --><div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Industry Partner Profile</p></div></div><div ><div><p>Be Challenged</p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>At Be Challenged, we&#8217;re redefining graduate programs by creating impactful experiences that build connections, simplify onboarding, and support managers in effectively leading their teams.</p><p><strong>Our methodology</strong></p><p>By combining traditional learning with experiential activities, we reinforce key concepts, catering to diverse learning styles and ensuring knowledge retention through hands-on, real-world applications.</p><p><strong>Our orientation week programs</strong></p><p>We curate a high-energy introduction to your organisational culture and values, setting the tone for success through interactive activities that build confidence, camaraderie, and a strong foundation for graduates.</p><p><strong>Our graduate conferences</strong></p><p>Infusing conference sessions with dynamic learning experiences, your graduates will be energised with interactive sessions that not only inspire but also translate into practical strategies for workplace success.</p><p><strong>Our Scope and Sequence approach</strong></p><p>Our team works closely with you to understand your objectives and to design a bespoke structured, long-term development plan that nurtures individual and team growth, ensuring sustained learning, engagement and measurable impact over time.</p><p><strong>Our whole of career experience</strong></p><p>At Be Challenged we work with clients at all stages of their career journeys and across a wide range of sectors. This experience enables us to design learning experiences that prepare your graduates for the various phases of their careers- not just the one they are in.</p><p><strong>Our Buzz</strong></p><p>All of our programs are delivered with the Be Challenged Buzz; which is the high level of energy and engagement that ensures your graduates will feel more connected to key messages, to one another and to your organisation.</p><p>For more information call 1300 723 476 or email <a href="mailto:team@bechallenged.com.au" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">team@bechallenged.com.au</a></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/1-be-challenged-172766ff-37a5985d.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div ><div><p>Contact details</p></div></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="mailto:team@bechallenged.com.au" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Email</a>&nbsp;<br></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="https://bechallenged.com.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Website</a>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="tel:+611300723476" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tel:&nbsp;1300 723 476</a></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
INSERT INTO pages (slug, title, content, requires_auth, show_in_nav, nav_position, published) VALUES ('shl', 'SHL', '<div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><h1>Helping shape the future of early careers through industry partnerships</h1></div></div><div ><div><a href="/page.html?slug=join-us" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Join us</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div><!-- /content zone --><!-- footer zone --><div><div><div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>AAGE Industry Partner Profile</p></div></div><div ><div><p>SHL</p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p>SHL is the only assessment partner that can benchmark your graduate applicants and hires against the very best candidates in the Australian market.</p><p>We are thrilled to partner with AAGE in 2026 and beyond as an AAGE Industry Partner.</p><p>Graduate leaders need a comprehensive set of solutions to identify and develop the right fit and highest potential graduates and SHL''s end-to-end platform delivers this through:</p><ul><li>Branded candidate experiences to stand out</li><li>Skills and cognitive ability assessments</li><li>On-demand or live video interviewing</li><li>An end-to-end scheduling and AI-empowered interviewing platform</li><li>Technical/coding assessments for future software engineers and data scientists</li><li>Virtual or in-person assessment centres</li><li>Individual and group cohort analytics and benchmarks</li></ul><p>For the <em>development </em>of graduates, we provide individual and group feedback so that your development initiatives can be precisely targeted and maximise the potential of your graduate cohort.</p> For more e-mail us at <a href="mailto:learnmore@shl.com" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">learnmore@shl.com</a>&nbsp;or go to <a href="https://www.shl.com/solutions/talent-acquisition/graduate/" target="_blank" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.shl.com/solutions/talent-acquisition/graduate/</a></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><img src="https://pr-9q32ba.run402.com/_blob/assets/aage/shl-logo-ad4689e6-06213d42.png" alt="" title="" loading="lazy"><br></p></div></div></div></div></td></tr></table></div><div ><div><p>Contact details</p></div></div><div><table><tr><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="mailto:learnmore@shl.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Email</a>&nbsp;<br></p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td><div><div><div ><div><p><a href="https://www.shl.com/solutions/talent-acquisition/graduate/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Website</a>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></td><td><div></div></td><td></td><td><div></div></td><td></td></tr></table></div><div><table><tr><td></td></tr></table></div></div></div></div>', false, false, NULL, true);
